<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Interactive Force Cueing Platform</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
:root{
  --red:#cc0000;--red2:#ff1a1a;--red-dim:rgba(204,0,0,0.12);
  --gold:#ffcc00;--gold2:#ffaa00;--gold-dim:rgba(255,204,0,0.12);
  --black:#111111;--black2:#1a1a1a;
  --surface:#222222;--surface2:#2a2a2a;--surface3:#333333;
  --text:#f0f0f0;--muted:#888888;--border:#333333;
  --green:#22c55e;--green-dim:rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
  --blue:#60a5fa;--blue-dim:rgba(96,165,250,0.1);
  --orange:#fb923c;--orange-dim:rgba(251,146,60,0.1);
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--black);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;line-height:1.6;}

/* ── HEADER ── */
.header{background:var(--red);padding:0 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:60px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(204,0,0,0.4);}
.header-brand{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:3px;color:#fff;}
.header-brand span{color:var(--gold);}
.header-sub{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;}

/* ── TAB NAV ── */
.tab-nav{background:var(--black2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 24px;display:flex;gap:4px;overflow-x:auto;}
.tab-btn{padding:14px 20px;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:all 0.15s;}
.tab-btn:hover{color:var(--text);}
.tab-btn.active{color:#fff;border-bottom-color:var(--gold);}

/* ── CONTENT ── */
.tab-content{display:none;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 64px;}
.tab-content.active{display:block;}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero-panel{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--black2) 0%,#1a0000 100%);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--red);border-radius:4px;padding:40px 32px;margin-bottom:24px;}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-block;background:var(--gold);color:#000;font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.hero-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem);letter-spacing:3px;color:#fff;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;}
.hero-title span{color:var(--red);}
.hero-sub{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--muted);}

/* ── FORMULA ── */
.formula-wrap{background:var(--black2);border:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:4px;padding:24px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px;}
.formula{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1rem,3vw,1.6rem);letter-spacing:2px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:16px;}
.formula span{color:var(--gold);}
.formula-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;}
.formula-item{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--red);border-radius:3px;padding:14px;}
.formula-item.gold{border-left-color:var(--gold);}
.formula-item-title{font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;}
.formula-item-desc{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);}

/* ── QUICK NAV CARDS ── */
.quick-nav{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.nav-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s;}
.nav-card:hover{background:var(--surface2);border-color:var(--red);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.nav-card-icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
.nav-card-title{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px;}
.nav-card-btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--red);color:#fff;font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:2px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.15s;}
.nav-card-btn:hover{background:var(--red2);}

/* ── CARDS ── */
.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.card-title{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:10px;}
.card-body{font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;}
.card-2col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.card-3col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;}

/* ── CALLOUTS ── */
.callout{border-radius:4px;padding:16px 18px;margin-bottom:14px;border-left:3px solid;}
.callout-red{background:var(--red-dim);border-color:var(--red);}
.callout-gold{background:var(--gold-dim);border-color:var(--gold);}
.callout-green{background:var(--green-dim);border-color:var(--green);}
.callout-blue{background:var(--blue-dim);border-color:var(--blue);}
.callout-title{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;}
.callout-red .callout-title{color:var(--red2);}
.callout-gold .callout-title{color:var(--gold);}
.callout-green .callout-title{color:var(--green);}
.callout-blue .callout-title{color:var(--blue);}
.callout p,.callout li{font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;}
.callout strong{color:var(--text);}
.callout ul{padding-left:18px;}
.callout li{margin-bottom:4px;}

/* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
.section-eyebrow{font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:6px;}
.section-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.8rem;letter-spacing:2px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:20px;}

/* ── FORCE CURVE ── */
.cue-selector{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.cue-btn{padding:10px 24px;border:2px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);color:var(--muted);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s;}
.cue-btn:hover{border-color:var(--muted);color:var(--text);}
.cue-btn.active-absorb{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue-dim);}
.cue-btn.active-feel{border-color:#a78bfa;color:#a78bfa;background:rgba(167,139,250,0.1);}
.cue-btn.active-attack{border-color:var(--red2);color:var(--red2);background:var(--red-dim);}
.curve-wrap{background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.curve-meta{text-align:center;margin-top:12px;}
.curve-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.curve-badge.absorb{background:var(--blue-dim);color:var(--blue);}
.curve-badge.feel{background:rgba(167,139,250,0.1);color:#a78bfa;}
.curve-badge.attack{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--red2);}
.curve-gct{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px;}
.animate-pulse-once{animation:pulseCurve 0.8s ease-in-out;}
@keyframes pulseCurve{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:0.3;}}

/* ── CUE COMPARISON CARDS ── */
.cue-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:18px;}
.cue-card-label{font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:10px;}
.cue-card-label.absorb{background:var(--blue-dim);color:var(--blue);}
.cue-card-label.feel{background:rgba(167,139,250,0.1);color:#a78bfa;}
.cue-card-label.attack{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--red2);}
.cue-card-quote{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:10px;}
.cue-card ul{list-style:none;padding:0;}
.cue-card li{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);padding:3px 0 3px 14px;position:relative;}
.cue-card li::before{content:'•';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--border);}

/* ── CONTINUUM BAR ── */
.continuum-bar{height:8px;background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--blue),#a78bfa,var(--red2));border-radius:4px;margin:16px 0 24px;}
.continuum-nodes{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;}
.c-node{text-align:center;cursor:pointer;}
.c-dot{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:#fff;margin:0 auto 6px;transition:transform 0.15s;border:2px solid transparent;}
.c-dot:hover{transform:scale(1.1);}
.c-dot.absorb{background:var(--blue);}
.c-dot.feel{background:#7c3aed;}
.c-dot.attack{background:var(--red);}
.c-label{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);}

/* ── ISOMETRIC CARDS ── */
.iso-card{background:var(--surface);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:20px;transition:all 0.15s;}
.iso-card:hover{border-color:var(--red);}
.iso-card-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.iso-card-badge.hima{background:var(--blue-dim);color:var(--blue);}
.iso-card-badge.pima{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--red2);}
.iso-card-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.3rem;letter-spacing:2px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:6px;}
.iso-card p{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px;}
.iso-visual{text-align:center;padding:16px 0;font-size:2rem;}
.iso-inner{background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:12px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.iso-inner-title{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px;}
.iso-inner ul{list-style:none;padding:0;}
.iso-inner li{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);padding:2px 0 2px 14px;position:relative;}
.iso-inner li::before{content:'—';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--border);}

/* ── PLYOMETRIC PHASES ── */
.plyo-phases{display:flex;gap:8px;overflow-x:auto;padding-bottom:12px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.plyo-phase{flex-shrink:0;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:12px 14px;text-align:center;min-width:120px;}
.plyo-phase-name{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;}
.plyo-phase-stage{font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);}
.plyo-phase.p1{border-top:3px solid var(--green);}
.plyo-phase.p2{border-top:3px solid var(--blue);}
.plyo-phase.p3{border-top:3px solid #a78bfa;}
.plyo-phase.p4{border-top:3px solid var(--red2);}
.plyo-phase.p5{border-top:3px solid var(--orange);}
.plyo-arrow{flex-shrink:0;color:var(--border);font-size:1.2rem;align-self:center;}

/* ── QUIZ BLOCK ── */
.quiz-block{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:20px;}
.quiz-q{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:6px;}
.quiz-scenario{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px;}
.quiz-opt{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;width:100%;text-align:left;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.82rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.5;}
.quiz-opt:hover:not(.disabled){background:var(--surface2);border-color:var(--muted);}
.quiz-opt.correct{border-color:var(--green);background:var(--green-dim);color:var(--text);}
.quiz-opt.wrong{border-color:var(--red);background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--text);}
.quiz-opt.disabled{cursor:not-allowed;}
.quiz-feedback{border-radius:4px;padding:14px 16px;margin-top:12px;font-size:0.83rem;line-height:1.6;}
.quiz-feedback.correct{background:var(--green-dim);border:1px solid var(--green);color:var(--green);}
.quiz-feedback.wrong{background:var(--gold-dim);border:1px solid var(--gold);color:var(--gold);}
.quiz-reset{margin-top:12px;padding:8px 20px;background:var(--red);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:3px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;}
.quiz-reset:hover{background:var(--red2);}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .quick-nav{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .card-2col,.card-3col,.formula-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .header-sub{display:none;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="header-brand">Force <span>Cueing Platform</span></div>
  <div class="header-sub">Interactive · Clinical Application</div>
</header>

<!-- TAB NAV -->
<nav class="tab-nav">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('overview',this)">Overview</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('force',this)">Impulse vs Peak Force</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('continuum',this)">Cue Continuum</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('isometric',this)">Isometric Apps</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('plyometric',this)">Plyometric Apps</button>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- OVERVIEW                             -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-overview" class="tab-content active">
  <div class="hero-panel">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Interactive Learning Platform</div>
    <div class="hero-title">Cueing Makes <span>The Context</span></div>
    <div class="hero-sub">How language manipulates force production — clinical applications for rehab professionals</div>
  </div>

  <div class="formula-wrap">
    <div class="formula">Adaptation = Tissue Capacity × Exercise × <span>Cue Intent</span></div>
    <div class="formula-grid">
      <div class="formula-item">
        <div class="formula-item-title">Tissue Capacity</div>
        <div class="formula-item-desc">Current envelope of function — what the tissue can tolerate</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-item">
        <div class="formula-item-title">Exercise Type</div>
        <div class="formula-item-desc">Movement and load selection appropriate to the phase</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-item gold">
        <div class="formula-item-title" style="color:var(--gold);">Cue Intent</div>
        <div class="formula-item-desc">Language shapes force profile — the variable you control</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="quick-nav">
    <div class="nav-card" onclick="showTab('force',document.querySelector('.tab-btn:nth-child(2)'))">
      <div class="nav-card-icon">📈</div>
      <div class="nav-card-title">Impulse vs Peak Force</div>
      <button class="nav-card-btn">Explore →</button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-card" onclick="showTab('continuum',document.querySelector('.tab-btn:nth-child(3)'))">
      <div class="nav-card-icon">🎚️</div>
      <div class="nav-card-title">Cue Continuum</div>
      <button class="nav-card-btn">Explore →</button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-card" onclick="showTab('isometric',document.querySelector('.tab-btn:nth-child(4)'))">
      <div class="nav-card-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="nav-card-title">Isometric Apps</div>
      <button class="nav-card-btn">Explore →</button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-card" onclick="showTab('plyometric',document.querySelector('.tab-btn:nth-child(5)'))">
      <div class="nav-card-icon">🎯</div>
      <div class="nav-card-title">Plyometric Apps</div>
      <button class="nav-card-btn">Explore →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- FORCE CURVE                          -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-force" class="tab-content">
  <div class="section-eyebrow">Interactive Demo</div>
  <div class="section-title">Force-Time Curve Visualiser</div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="cue-selector">
      <button class="cue-btn active-absorb" id="btn-absorb" onclick="selectCue('absorb')">Absorb</button>
      <button class="cue-btn" id="btn-feel" onclick="selectCue('feel')">Feel</button>
      <button class="cue-btn" id="btn-attack" onclick="selectCue('attack')">Attack</button>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <button onclick="animateCurve()" style="padding:10px 24px;background:var(--red);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:3px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;">▶ Animate Force Curve</button>
    </div>

    <div class="curve-wrap">
      <svg id="force-svg" viewBox="0 0 400 220" style="width:100%;display:block;background:var(--black);">
        <!-- Grid lines -->
        <line x1="40" y1="180" x2="370" y2="180" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="180" x2="40" y2="30" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="130" x2="370" y2="130" stroke="#222" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="80" x2="370" y2="80" stroke="#222" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
        <!-- Axis labels -->
        <text x="205" y="200" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#666" font-family="Inter">Time</text>
        <text x="18" y="110" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#666" font-family="Inter" transform="rotate(-90 18 110)">Force</text>
        <!-- Curve path -->
        <path id="force-curve" d="" fill="none" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <!-- Fill -->
        <path id="force-fill" d="" fill-opacity="0.15"/>
        <!-- Peak dot -->
        <circle id="peak-dot" cx="0" cy="0" r="6" opacity="0"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="curve-meta">
        <div class="curve-badge absorb" id="curve-badge">High Impulse, Low Peak Force</div>
        <div class="curve-gct" id="curve-gct">Ground Contact Time: ~500ms</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-3col">
      <div class="cue-card">
        <div class="cue-card-label absorb">Absorb</div>
        <div class="cue-card-quote">"Land soft and slow"</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Long contact time</li>
          <li>Low peak force</li>
          <li>High total impulse</li>
          <li>Early rehab focus</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="cue-card">
        <div class="cue-card-label feel">Feel</div>
        <div class="cue-card-quote">"Feel the ground, then push"</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Moderate contact time</li>
          <li>Moderate peak force</li>
          <li>Balanced profile</li>
          <li>Mid-stage focus</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="cue-card">
        <div class="cue-card-label attack">Attack</div>
        <div class="cue-card-quote">"Attack and explode"</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Short contact time</li>
          <li>High peak force</li>
          <li>Low total impulse</li>
          <li>Performance focus</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- CONTINUUM                            -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-continuum" class="tab-content">
  <div class="section-eyebrow">Intensity Scale</div>
  <div class="section-title">Cue Intensity Continuum</div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="continuum-bar"></div>
    <div class="continuum-nodes">
      <div class="c-node" onclick="highlightContinuum('absorb')">
        <div class="c-dot absorb">0</div>
        <div class="c-label">Absorb</div>
      </div>
      <div class="c-node" onclick="highlightContinuum('feel')">
        <div class="c-dot feel">50</div>
        <div class="c-label">Feel</div>
      </div>
      <div class="c-node" onclick="highlightContinuum('attack')">
        <div class="c-dot attack">100</div>
        <div class="c-label">Attack</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="continuum-detail" style="margin-top:20px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Same Exercise, Different Cues — Calf Raise</div>
    <div class="card-3col" style="margin-top:12px;">
      <div style="background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--blue);border-radius:3px;padding:14px;">
        <div style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:6px;">ENDURANCE GOAL</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:8px;">"Gently press up and hold"</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);">→ High time under tension, metabolic stress</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid #a78bfa;border-radius:3px;padding:14px;">
        <div style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#a78bfa;margin-bottom:6px;">HYPERTROPHY GOAL</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:8px;">"Gradually crush upward"</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);">→ Controlled force development, mechanical tension</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--red2);border-radius:3px;padding:14px;">
        <div style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--red2);margin-bottom:6px;">POWER GOAL</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:8px;">"Explode up through ceiling"</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);">→ Rapid force production, rate of force development</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="callout callout-gold">
    <div class="callout-title">Key Takeaway</div>
    <p>The same exercise prescribes entirely different adaptations depending on the cue intent. <strong>Cue intent is a programmable variable</strong> — not just motivational language.</p>
  </div>
</div>

